  "title": "Sales Engineer/Quantity Surveyor - Mechanical and Electrical (M&E)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br /><br />1. Solicits new customer/products, existing customer’s recommendation and other sources which provide regular updates on construction projects</p><p>2. Review Mechanical and Electrical (M&E- Electrical) tender documents and drawing</p><p>3. Material takes off, prepare bill of quantities and cost estimation</p><p>4. Prepare technical data quotation and proposal to clients</p><p>5. Attend to site visits/offices for contract negotiation</p><p>6. Collects and collates background and ongoing project information of new customers to better facilitate credit approval</p><p>7. Analyzes reports which helps to increases sales revenue and achieve profitability</p><p>8. Other ad-hoc activities assigned by superior<br /><br /><br /><strong>Job Qualifications:</strong></p><p><strong>Education Required:</strong></p><p>• Diploma/Degree in Quantity Surveying, Electrical Engineering<br /></p><p><strong>Experience Required:</strong></p><p>• Min 2 years in Electrical sector</p><p>• Working experience as Electrical QS is preferred</p><p>•Proficiency in MS Office & Auto CAD<br /></p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
